---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Win-Win Apps collects, uses, and protects your data." current="">
  <section class="hero"><div class="container container-narrow"><p class="eyebrow">Legal</p><h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p class="hero-lead">Last updated April 22, 2026.</p></div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="container container-narrow prose">
    <p>Win-Win Apps (we, us, our) operates wwapps.io and the apps listed on the Shopify App Store. This policy explains what data we collect and how we use it.</p>
    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>We collect only what is needed to operate our apps. For most of our apps this means store domain, app configuration, and anonymous usage metrics. We never sell data to third parties.</p>
    <h2>Data retention</h2>
    <p>If you uninstall an app, your configuration data is deleted within 30 days, per Shopify's app data retention policies.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For any privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:privacy@wwapps.io">privacy@wwapps.io</a>.</p>
  </div></section>
</BaseLayout>
